oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Nora Ella Scott
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Edwin Best
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Greenback (Tenn.); Scott, (Nora) Ella;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A thirteen-year-old girl stands beside a tree with overhanging leaves, in the backyard of the Alleghany House hotel. Her hair has a bow. With her skirt and blouse, she's wearing heavy stockings and laced shoes. Business buildings are in the background.
